title: Kirstie's.Fill.Your.House.For.Free.2013.SWESUB.720p.WEBRip.H264-
description:
Series 1 Summary
Kirstie Allsopp helps people transform their homes with furniture that's been sourced for free.

Episode 1 - Harry & Gillian and Sarah
Secondhand is definitely not second best, as Kirstie Allsopp kits out two homes with free-sourced and upcycled furniture and fittings.

Episode 2 - Curt & Nicola and Jules
Kirstie and the team help young couple Curt and Nicola kit out their first flat together on a zero price tag. They also help transform Jules Pritchard's family snug after it's been flooded.

Episode 3 - Liz & Stephen and Alistair & Charlotte
Kirstie and co help Liz and Stephen source some sturdy, stylish pieces for their family home in Kent. They also kit out London couple Alistair Bray and Charlotte Campbell's bedroom.

Episode 4 - Zoe & Gavin and Gillian
Kirstie and the team help Zoe and Gavin make their new house into a home on a shoestring. And they also get to work on Gillian Brabin's bathroom.
